(1, '2023-09-27 20:24:48.110', '2024-03-05 16:33:16.008', 901, 'Enjoy the convenience of a room that offers both combined and separate bed options, tailored to your preference. Located near the breakfast area, this room is equipped with all essentials for a comfortable stay. Ideal for guests who value flexibility in sleeping arrangements and easy access to morning dining.', '["901/abd00363-hdr.webp", "901/abd00354-hdr.webp", "901/abd00326.webp", "901/abd00311.webp", "901/abd00323.webp"]', 2, 1, 3),
(2, '2023-09-27 20:25:38.882', '2024-03-03 14:54:34.630', 902, 'This 23 square meter room combines snug comfort with an extraordinary city view. Perfect for guests seeking a warm, intimate space with the luxury of a stunning urban outlook. Despite its smaller size, the room provides a grand view of the city, making it a top pick for those who enjoy cozy accommodations with a touch of expansive elegance.', '["901/abd00270-hdr.webp", "901/abd00354-hdr.webp", "901/abd00353.webp", "901/abd00323.webp", "901/abd00311.webp"]', 2, 1, 4),
(3, '2023-09-27 20:26:34.663', '2024-03-05 13:09:32.517', 903, 'Ideal for those who desire unparalleled views of the city, this suite offers a stunning panorama from every vantage point. Whether you''re out on the balcony or inside the room, you''re treated to a unique and breathtaking cityscape, making it the perfect choice for a truly scenic and memorable stay.', '["903/abd00376-hdr.webp", "903/abd00381-hdr.webp", "903/abd00323.webp", "903/abd00311.webp", "903/abd00405-hdr.webp", "903/abd00426.webp"]', 2, 1, 5),
(4, '2023-09-27 20:28:03.200', '2024-03-05 16:33:27.778', 904, 'Experience Tbilisi like never before in our deluxe double room, where the city''s heart unfolds right before your eyes. The balcony presents an unparalleled view, offering a rare glimpse into the vibrant life of the old city. It''s more than just a room; it''s a window to the soul of Tbilisi, held in the palm of your hand.', '["904/abd00461-hdr.webp", "904/abd00475-hdr.webp", "904/abd00326.webp", "904/abd00445-hdr.webp", "904/abd00311.webp"]', 2, 1, 6),
(5, '2023-09-27 20:29:21.123', '2024-03-06 05:52:04.129', 905, 'Nestled in the heart of the old city, this deluxe double room with a balcony brings the best of Tbilisi to your doorstep. The view is extraordinary, capturing the essence of the city in a way that''s seldom seen. Here, Tbilisi isn''t just a view; it''s an experience, right there for you to grasp.', '["904/abd00326.webp", "904/abd00323.webp", "904/abd00311.webp", "904/abd00445-hdr.webp", "904/abd00456-hdr.webp", "904/abd00475-hdr.webp"]', 2, 1, 7),
(6, '2023-09-27 20:29:57.171', '2024-03-05 16:33:37.811', 906, 'This double room offers more than comfort; it''s a gateway to the past. From the balcony, enjoy the serene view of Mtatsminda, complemented by a staircase that showcases the quaint charm of old Tbilisi architecture. It''s a perfect blend of scenic beauty and vintage aesthetics, offering a unique window into the city''s soul.', '["906/abd00326.webp", "906/abd00311.webp", "906/abd00490-hdr.webp", "906/abd00481-hdr.webp"]', 2, 1, 8),
(7, '2023-09-27 20:30:41.564', '2024-03-05 16:33:51.634', 907, 'This room provides the unique option of either joined or individual beds, catering to various needs and preferences. Situated close to the breakfast area, it''s well-equipped with all the necessities for a comfortable and convenient stay, perfect for those who appreciate quick access to breakfast and adaptable sleeping options.', '["907/abd00499-hdr.webp", "907/abd00493-hdr.webp", "907/abd00326.webp", "907/abd00323.webp", "907/abd00311.webp"]', 2, 1, 9),
(8, '2023-09-27 23:57:58.894', '2024-03-05 16:33:01.488', 802, 'Our 23 square meter double room is a cozy haven, offering a unique and expansive view of the cityscape from its windows. It''s the ideal choice for those who appreciate the intimacy of a smaller space paired with the grandeur of a vast, beautiful urban panorama. Experience comfort and charm with a spectacular view, all in a compact setting.', '["802/abd00582.webp", "802/abd00570-hdr.webp", "802/abd00576.webp", "802/abd00596.webp"]', 2, 1, 11),
(9, '2023-09-27 23:58:48.462', '2024-03-05 16:34:06.537', 803, 'Be captivated by our unique 30 square meter suite, designed to amaze at every turn. It features a luxurious Jacuzzi set against a backdrop of panoramic city views. This unorthodox hotel room is an extraordinary retreat, perfect for those seeking an exceptional and surprising experience.', '["803/abd01780-hdr.webp", "803/abd01777-hdr.webp", "803/abd01791.webp", "803/abd01792.webp"]', 2, 1, 12),
(10, '2023-09-28 00:00:57.861', '2024-03-05 16:34:51.765', 804, 'Designed for those who seek exceptional comfort, this junior suite offers a stunning city view from its balcony. Immerse yourself in the elegance of this space, where every detail caters to your comfort and the panorama outside your window captivates and delights.', '["804/abd00630.webp", "804/abd00600-hdr.webp", "804/abd00633.webp", "804/abd00618.webp"]', 2, 1, 13),
(11, '2023-09-28 00:02:10.022', '2024-03-05 16:35:53.685', 806, 'Our 35 square meter king room is a haven for those who love options and nature. Choose from cozy single beds or a grand king-size bed to suit your comfort. The highlight is the balcony, opening up to spectacular mountain vistas, offering a serene and picturesque escape. Perfect for guests who desire a blend of majestic scenery and flexible sleeping options.', '["806/abd00659-hdr.webp", "806/abd00684.webp", "806/abd00672.webp", "806/abd01959.webp", "806/abd01956-hdr.webp"]', 2, 1, 15),
(12, '2023-09-28 00:03:22.585', '2024-03-05 16:36:21.991', 701, 'Experience the charm of our Junior Suite, extending over 36 square meters. This suite is an ideal retreat for families or small teams, offering a spacious king-size bed in the main bedroom and a single bed in a separate room. Designed to cater to both work and relaxation needs, the suite captivates with its remarkable view of the old city''s skyline. While it doesn''t feature a balcony, the enchanting cityscape view ensures a delightful and luxurious stay.', '["701/abd01801-hdr.webp", "701/abd01804-hdr.webp", "701/abd01816.webp", "701/abd01813.webp"]', 3, 1, 16),
(13, '2023-09-28 00:04:15.831', '2024-03-05 16:36:32.933', 702, 'Immerse yourself in 35 square meters of tranquility, featuring an inviting open balcony that frames a stunning cityscape. The highlight of this room is its luxurious hot tub. Imagine unwinding in warm, soothing waters while gazing out at the historic beauty of old Tbilisi. This room is the epitome of relaxation, offering a unique blend of comfort and scenic views, perfect for those seeking a serene escape.', '["702/abd01850-hdr.webp", "702/abd01859.webp", "702/abd01869-hdr.webp", "702/abd01870-hdr.webp"]', 2, 1, 17),
(14, '2023-09-28 00:05:15.967', '2024-03-05 16:36:44.437', 703, 'Spanning 35 square meters, this junior suite blends classic elegance with modern comforts. Step onto your private balcony to enjoy panoramic views of the city''s skyline. The room''s vintage design adds a touch of grandeur and coziness, creating an atmosphere of luxury with a hint of nostalgia. Ideal for those who appreciate the finer things in life while enjoying the vibrant cityscape.', '["703/abd01900-hdr.webp", "703/abd01923-hdr.webp", "703/abd01922.webp", "703/abd01926.webp"]', 2, 1, 18),
(15, '2023-09-28 00:05:54.107', '2024-03-05 16:37:12.188', 704, 'Discover the luxury of space in our 38 square meter junior suite. Featuring a balcony that offers a magnificent view of the city, this suite is a perfect fusion of function and elegance. Ideal for guests who seek a balance between work and leisure, it''s a space where comfort meets breathtaking urban vistas, ensuring a stay that is both productive and relaxing.', '["704/abd01947.webp", "704/abd01944.webp", "704/abd01935.webp"]', 2, 1, 19),
(16, '2023-11-20 21:57:50.695', '2024-03-05 16:34:19.064', 801, 'Our generously sized Junior Suite, covering more than 36 square meters, is designed with families and small groups in mind. It features a luxurious king-size bed in the primary bedroom and a comfortable single bed in an adjacent room. Perfect for balancing work and leisure, the suite offers a stunning panorama of the old city from its windows, providing a serene backdrop. Although it lacks a balcony, the breathtaking view more than compensates, ensuring a memorable stay.', '["801/abd00516-hdr.webp", "801/abd00550-hdr.webp", "801/abd00531-hdr.webp", "801/abd00544.webp", "801/abd00532-hdr.webp", "801/abd00541.webp"]', 2, 1, 10),
(17, '2023-11-20 22:03:33.181', '2024-03-05 16:36:54.893', 705, 'Spanning 35 square meters, this versatile room caters to all preferences, offering the choice between single beds or a luxurious king-size bed. Step out onto the balcony to be greeted by the awe-inspiring views of the mountains. This room is an ideal retreat for those who appreciate natural beauty and seek a comfortable, adaptable sleeping arrangement.', '["806/abd00659-hdr.webp", "806/abd01956-hdr.webp", "806/abd00684.webp", "806/abd01959.webp", "806/abd00672.webp"]', 2, 1, 20),
(18, '2023-11-20 22:06:55.694', '2024-03-05 16:35:34.510', 805, 'Tailored for comfort enthusiasts, this junior suite provides an extraordinary vantage point to enjoy the city''s skyline from its balcony. Experience the fusion of luxury and scenic beauty, perfect for those who appreciate a room that not only comforts but also inspires with its breathtaking views.', '["804/abd00633.webp", "804/abd00600-hdr.webp", "804/abd00630.webp", "804/abd00618.webp"]', 2, 1, 14),
(19, '2023-11-20 22:22:53.514', '2024-03-05 16:37:34.838', 201, 'Nestled in the historic center, this budget-friendly double room offers all the essential comforts for a pleasant stay. It''s a perfect blend of modern amenities and affordability, right in the midst of the old city''s charm.', '["201/6.webp", "201/1.webp", "201/3.webp", "201/2.webp"]', 2, 1, 21),
